Quick Start / 快速开始
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Double-click "Start.bat" to launch the application
   双击 "Start.bat" 启动应用

2. Wait for the browser to open automatically (about 2-3 seconds)
   等待浏览器自动打开（约2-3秒）

3. Enter Japanese text in the browser to analyze
   在浏览器中输入日语文本进行分析

4. Press Ctrl+C in the console window to stop the server
   在控制台窗口按 Ctrl+C 停止服务器


System Requirements / 系统要求
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

- Windows 7 or higher (64-bit recommended)
- No Python installation required (embedded runtime included)
- About 100MB disk space
- Internet browser (Chrome, Firefox, Edge, etc.)


Features / 功能特性
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

- Japanese morphological analysis using Sudachi
- Web-based user interface
- Support for multiple display columns
- Real-time text analysis
- No installation required


Troubleshooting / 故障排除
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Q: Nothing happens when I double-click Start.bat?
A: Check if port 8000 is occupied. The app will try to clear it automatically.

Q: Browser doesn't open automatically?
A: Manually open: http://127.0.0.1:8000

Q: How to change the port?
A: Edit WebSudachi\WebSudachi.int, change PORT = 8000 to another value

Q: Need to reinstall dependencies?
A: Run WebSudachi\setup_dependencies.bat


